OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FFoster carers are "walking angels" who
OL,7,Fcan change a child's life, Traitors
OL,8,Fstar Roxy Wilson has told ITV News -
OL,9,Fbut there is a serious shortage of
OL,10,Fthem in the UK, according to the
OL,11,FDepartment for Education (DfE).
OL,13,FRoxy spent the first few years of her
OL,14,Flife in foster care, being passed from
OL,15,Ffamily to family, before she was
OL,16,Feventually adopted by Judy Wilson who
OL,17,Fwould become her mum and eventually
OL,18,Fher Traitors co-star.
