OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FRoxy and Judy are both speaking out in
OL,7,Fsupport of fostering in a bid to
OL,8,Fencourage more people to become foster
OL,9,Fcarers, while the government relaxes
OL,10,Fthe rules to make it easier.
OL,12,FDespite the number of children in care
OL,13,Fbeing at a "historic high", approved
OL,14,Fcarer numbers have fallen by almost
OL,15,F12% over the past decade.
