OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FPressure on the system means
OL,7,Fvulnerable children can end up being
OL,8,Fmoved from family to family, often
OL,9,Fmany miles away from where they grew
OL,10,Fup, sometimes in residential care
OL,11,Fhomes, which can be extremely damaging
OL,12,Fto their development.
OL,14,F"I was passed around quite a lot in
OL,15,Ffoster care, so maybe like five or six
OL,16,Fdifferent carers," Roxy said, "so it
OL,17,Fwas a difficult start to life... it's
OL,18,Fquite sad, but it just becomes your
OL,19,Fnormal life."
