OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FRoxy and Judy from the Traitors spoke
OL,7,Fto ITV News Reporter Lewis Denison
OL,8,Fabout foster care
OL,10,FShe added: "The trauma of being moved
OL,11,Faround all the time, the trauma of not
OL,12,Fhaving biological parents that will do
OL,13,Fthings to a child, which will cause
OL,14,Fthem to have challenges."
OL,16,FThe government wants to create an
OL,17,Fextra 10,000 foster care places by
OL,18,F2029 to ensure as many children as
OL,19,Fpossible can find loving homes without
OL,20,Fbeing regularly moved around.
