OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FRule changes being considered could
OL,7,Fallow single people, renters and those
OL,8,Fin full-time work to become foster
OL,9,Fcarers across England - many of those
OL,10,Fgroups are banned from fostering in
OL,11,Fseveral local authorities.
OL,13,FRoxy's mum Judy said "anyone who's got
OL,14,Fa heart" should consider fostering
OL,15,Fbecause welcoming a child into her
OL,16,Fhome was "the best thing I ever did".
OL,18,F"Open up your arms, that's all you
OL,19,Fneed to do, and just give them love,"
OL,20,Fshe added.
