OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FRoxy said foster carers are "like
OL,7,Fwalking angels" who are "really
OL,8,Fchanging kids lives".
OL,10,F"They're not just to be forgotten
OL,11,Fabout. Like they need recognition.
OL,12,FThey need support in the sense of
OL,13,Ffinance, psychological support,
OL,14,Feverything that goes with it."
OL,16,FJudy agreed, telling ITV News "there's
OL,17,Fgot to be a lot more support out there
OL,18,Ffor the foster carers" and adding: "We
OL,19,Fwant a change."
