OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FThe DfE said #88 million of funding,
OL,7,Frepurposed from existing budgets, will
OL,8,Fbe channelled into supporting foster
OL,9,Fcarers and frontline services which
OL,10,Fhelp them - but the National Union of
OL,11,FProfessional Foster Carers said more
OL,12,Fshould be done.
OL,14,FRobin Findlay, the union's general
OL,15,Fsecretary, welcomed the government
OL,16,F"taking on the challenge of updating a
OL,17,Ffostering system which has been
OL,18,Fneglected for years" but said foster
OL,19,Fcarers should be given special worker
OL,20,Fstatus to properly protect them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
