OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,F"We feel that new and existing carers
OL,7,Fwill only feel properly supported if
OL,8,Fthey have the protection of a special
OL,9,Fworker status, in which they can still
OL,10,Fremain self employed but which will
OL,11,Fgive them proper rights if they are
OL,12,Ftreated incorrectly. Only with this
OL,13,Frespect will foster carers remain for
OL,14,Fa long time," he said.
