OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FChildren's Minister Josh MacAlister
OL,7,Ftold ITV News the number of children
OL,8,Fin care is at a "historic high" but
OL,9,Fcurrent rules mean "tens of thousands"
OL,10,Fof potential foster carers are being
OL,11,Fturned away, causing children in care
OL,12,Fto be moved on too far from home.
OL,14,FThe Department for Education said
OL,15,Fapproved carer numbers have fallen by
OL,16,Falmost 12% over the past decade, with
OL,17,Fa sharp fall since the coronavirus
OL,18,Fpandemic, and at the same time the
OL,19,Fnumber of children in care has
OL,20,Fincreased.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
