OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FMr MacAlister said: "We've got
OL,7,Fchildren living in children's homes
OL,8,Ffar away from where they've grown up,
OL,9,Fand that there are big risks in that
OL,10,Fbecause that's where we've seen lots
OL,11,Fof activity from grooming gangs and
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,F"So the current system, the default,
OL,15,Fisn't safe. We need to change that so
OL,16,Fwe get more loving families for these
OL,17,Fchildren."
OL,19,F"The current system isn't safe," says
OL,20,FChildrens' Minister Josh MacAlister
