OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FAhead of a consultation on changes to
OL,7,Fthe rules being published on
OL,8,FWednesday, Mr MacAlister said the
OL,9,Fproposals would bring fostering "into
OL,10,Fthe 21st century, removing outdated
OL,11,Frules and unnecessary barriers" to
OL,12,Fcaring.
OL,14,FHe added: "Reversing the decline in
OL,15,Fthe number of available foster places
OL,16,Fis an urgent priority for me because
OL,17,Ffostering is so vital to our mission
OL,18,Fto give children the best possible
OL,19,Fstart in life.
