OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,F"We're bringing fostering into the
OL,7,F21st century, removing outdated rules
OL,8,Fand unnecessary barriers to become
OL,9,Ffoster carers as part of our overhaul
OL,10,Fof the care system.
OL,12,F"Foster carers give children the
OL,13,Fstable, loving relationships they need
OL,14,Fto thrive. If you've ever considered
OL,15,Ffostering, I would urge you to look
OL,16,Finto this incredible vocation that can
OL,17,Ftransform a child's life."
