OL,3,C'Open up your arms': Traitors pair
OL,4,Curge people to become foster carers
OL,6,FSarah Thomas, chief executive of The
OL,7,FFostering Network, said: "We're really
OL,8,Fpleased to see this much-needed focus
OL,9,Fon foster care.
OL,11,F"For the past four years, more foster
OL,12,Fcarers have been leaving than joining,
OL,13,Fas increasing pressures within an
OL,14,Foverstretched children's social care
OL,15,Fsystem continue to impact on children."
